                        <div class="code-block">
                            SET-SIZE=SMALL
                        </div>
                        <p class="pl-3">
                            - Overrides the character's size (determined by their ancestry) with the new size.
                        </p>
                        <p class="pl-3">
                            - Options are: TINY, SMALL, MEDIUM, LARGE, HUGE, and GARGANTUAN.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
